    <item>
      <title>Attending the 2023 Heidelberg Laureate Forum</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/post/2023-09-29-hlf/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Sep 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/post/2023-09-29-hlf/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I was selected to attend the 2023 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.heidelberg-laureate-forum.org/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Heidelberg Laureate Forum&lt;/a&gt; as a young researcher in the field of computer science. The event was held from September 24 - 29, 2023 in &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heidelberg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Heidelberg&lt;/a&gt;, Germany. Attendees included young researchers and laureates of the Abel Prize, ACM A.M. Turing Award, ACM Prize in Computing, Fields Medal, IMU Abacus Medal and Nevanlinna Prize.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The event was a unique mix of academic and cultural exploration, fostering interdisciplinary discussions and encouraging collaboration. Connecting with laureates and fellow young researchers, the forum left a lasting impact on me, providing inspiration and valuable connections.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I can absolutely recommend anyone interested to &lt;a href=&#34;https://application.heidelberg-laureate-forum.org/site/index.php&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;apply&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
