    <item>
      <title>Four papers accepted to SIGIR 2023</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/post/2023-04-05-sigir/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Apr 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/post/2023-04-05-sigir/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This year, I was fortunate enough to be involved in four papers accepted at SIGIR (2 full papers, 1 resource paper, and 1 demo paper).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;[resource] &lt;strong&gt;The Archive Query Log: Mining Millions of Search Result Pages of Hundreds of Search Engines from 25 Years of Web Archives&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1145/3539618.3591890&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;read paper&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2304.00413&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;arxiv preprint&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/webis_de/status/1643366684382621696&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;twitter thread&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;[full paper] &lt;strong&gt;Can ChatGPT Write a Good Boolean Query for Systematic Review Literature Search?&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1145/3539618.3591703&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;read paper&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2302.03495&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;arxiv preprint&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hscells/status/1643558762152701954&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;twitter thread&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
