    <item>
      <title>Universities Australia – DAAD Joint Research Co-operation Scheme</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/post/2022-11-22-daadppp/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Nov 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/post/2022-11-22-daadppp/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We are &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.universitiesaustralia.edu.au/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/2022-UA-Website-Update-Successful-Applications.pdf&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;one of the 45 projects&lt;/a&gt; awarded funding under the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.universitiesaustralia.edu.au/policy-submissions/international/australia-germany-joint-research-co-operation-scheme/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Universities Australia – DAAD Joint Research Co-operation Scheme&lt;/a&gt;. This scheme facilitates the exchange of early career researchers in Australia and Germany from early 2023 until the end of 2024. The &lt;a href=&#34;https://ielab.io&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;ielab&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://webis.de&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;webis&lt;/a&gt; research groups will be hosting researchers from Australia and Germany for two months at a time. The following researchers will be visiting ielab and webis across the two years:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2023:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://wshuai190.github.io/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Shuai Wang&lt;/a&gt; from The University of Queensland, Australia.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/fschlatt&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Ferdinand Schlatt&lt;/a&gt; from Friedrich-Schiller-Universität Jena, Germany.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2024:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://ielab.io/people/xinyu-mao&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Xinyu Mao&lt;/a&gt; from The University of Queensland, Australia&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://maik-froebe.de/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Maik Fröbe&lt;/a&gt; from Friedrich-Schiller-Universität Jena, Germany.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The project involves the two groups working together to automate the searching and screening phases of systematic review creation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For news about the project, publications, or other activities, please see the &lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/project/ua-daad-ppp-23&#34;&gt;project website&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
